(461, 1, '2017-05-11 05:12:53', '2017-05-11 05:12:53', '<h2>Multi-Dimension Logarithmic Number System Digital Filter Bank</h2>\r\nA new filterbank processor algorithm for a digital hearing instrument based on the Multi-Dimensional Logarithmic Number System (MDLNS) with a low power structure. The processor has integrated binary to MDLNS converters. The design has been optimized for timing; testing shows very competitive power comsumption and area requirements to current binary filter banks. Implemented on TSMCs 0.18祄 CMOS process.\r\n\r\nPrimary Designers: Hongbo (Jennifer) Li\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-463\" src=\"http://localhost/RCIM_lab/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/ICFWRDFB.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" />', 'ICFWRDFB', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '461', '', '', '2017-05-11 05:25:18', '2017-05-11 05:25:18', '', 0, 'http://localhost/RCIM_lab/?p=461', 0, 'post', '', 0),
